                    ]
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        },
        {
            "_id": "WgoHepdbZjSlxrPo",
            "img": "systems/pf2e/icons/default-icons/action.svg",
            "name": "Pick a Card, Any Card",
            "sort": 800000,
            "system": {
                "actionType": {
                    "value": "action"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>Mister Moxie designates an adjacent living creature who must pick a card from his deck of harrow cards. The chosen creature finds a phantasmal duplicate deck of cards in their hand and is compelled by fate to draw a card; it can and must do so even if its hands are full, or it's unable to act. The creature rolls [[/gmr 1d6#suit]] to determine the suit of the card drawn to determine the effect (or if you have a harrow deck handy, have the player draw a card to determine the suit).</p>\n<p><strong>1—Hammer:</strong> (void) The target becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 1} for 24 hours.</p>\n<p><strong>2—Key:</strong> The target becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Quickened] for 1 minute and can use the extra action each round to Stride or Strike.</p>\n<p><strong>3—Shield:</strong> (void) The target becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Drained]{Drained 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>4—Tome:</strong> (void) The target becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Stupefied]{Stupefied 1} for 24 hours.</p>\n<p><strong>5—Star:</strong> (healing, vitality) The target regains 20 HP.</p>\n<p><strong>6—Crown:</strong> (emotion, mental) The target becomes @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Confused] for 1 minute.</p>"
                },
                "publication": {
                    "license": "OGL",
                    "remaster": false,
                    "title": ""
                },
                "rules": [],
                "slug": null,
                "traits": {
                    "value": [
                        "occult"
                    ]
                }
            },
            "type": "action"
        },
